data.name: richTextBox1.Text
data.value:
- You can use some templates for content (Title, Description, Url, Keywords) such as: {File} for File name, {FILE} for File name in UPPERCASE, {Random} for a random number. - Images will be resized and re-allocated into printable area corresponding to each platform. If original size of image is larger than printable area, it will be resized automatically. You can see sample in right box. - Stop uploading will not take effect immediately. It just stops after completing current processing design. - Application must run when sepecific time comes for Auto Start function works properly. - Auto Start function won't run if specific time comes and there is running upload process. - After Auto Start runs, that option will be disabled automatically. If you want to do auto start again, you must enable it manually. - Region should be chosen before adding garments to list.
CAUTION: - Preview images are used as reference only. Final results might have slight difference according to platforms. For some platforms, such as Teespring or Teechip, the smallest printabled box of all garments will be used.
CHANGE LOGS:
* August 2, 2017: - NEW: Auto post mockups to Facebook Pages - NEW: Allow to choose Teezily product's categories - Fix Teespring product's category - Fix minor bugs
* May 20, 2017: - Fix bug Sunfrog campaigns cannot be updated Facebook Pixel or Google Analytics in some cases. - Fix bug of uploading design for back side on Teezily
* May 15, 2017 - NEW: Add Teezily platform - NEW: Allow to import accounts from file - Fix wrong position of image on back side for Teechip and Viralstyle
* April 24, 2017 - Fix loading saved job bug - Fix error to retrieve Sunfrog campaign links for many colors uploads - Update to get only default campaign link for Sunfrog platform - Improve Mockup creation methods
* April 14, 2017 - Allow to create isolated campaign (private campaign) on Sunfrog - Allow to set Facebook Pixel ID for campaign on Sunfrog - Allow to set Category, Facebook Pixel ID and Google Analytics ID for campaign on Teespring - Allow to set Facebook Pixel ID, Google Analytics ID for campaign on Teechip - Allow to set Category, Facebook Pixel ID for campaign on Viralstyle
* April 4, 2017 - Auto Mockup: fix issues for some templates - Teespring: Colors of Mug will be counted as 1 now
* March 10, 2017 - NEW FEATURE: Mockup creatiion - Fix issues of loading Teespring resources
* February 26, 2017 - Critical: Fix bug of loading Sunfrog products - Critical: Fix bug of Teespring upload
* January 20, 2017 - Critical: Fix design position and size of Hoddie on Viralstyle - Critical: Fix Teespring upload - NEW: Allow to separate uploads to multiple accounts
* December 20, 2016 - Allow to configure delay time between uploads - Fix some minor bugs
* November 07, 2016 - Critical: Fix mis-aligned design of back side for Teespring - Set default template values for Title, Description, Keyword and Url
* November 03, 2016 - Critical: Fix mis-aligned design for combination of garments
* November 01, 2016 - Critical: Fix Teespring upload for EU region - Allow auto-extend for Viralstyle
* October 09, 2016 - Critical: Fix Sunfrog upload
* October 07, 2016 - Update: Allow to choose region for Teespring campaigns
* October 06, 2016 - Critical: Update to new Sunfrog's upload - Update: Can set Auto Relaunch and Private mode for Teespring - Fix: content template can be retrieved from Back image's name - Allow to Create information template and Apply it to existing designs - Allow to Save created campaigns into files manually or automatically - Allow to Auto Start uploading at specific time - Allow to Auto Rerun if any fail happens
* September 15, 2016 - Critical: Fix Viralstyle upload error - Add "Stop Uploading" - Make "Remove arts from list after upload" as default
* September 10, 2016 - Critical: Update Viralstyle new upload process - Critical: Fix overflow issue of some kinds of image on Teechip
* September 9, 2016: - Critical: update to bypass multiple-upload blocking of Viralstyle - Set AutoExtend of Viralstyle to False as default
